STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-respondent,
v.
Keith M. KENION, Defendant-petitioner. C-866 September Term 2017
080573 Supreme Court of New Jersey. May 21, 2018

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-001883-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
